\( \displaystyle 20 - t = 20 + t \)?$BR",
"Yes",
"Is \( t = 0 \) a solution to the equation
\( \displaystyle t+1 = \frac{1-t}{t} \)?$BR",
"No",
);

$tf->choose(5);


